title: Baseball legend Strawberry describes how God restored his life (Liberty University)
text: ( Source : Liberty University ) October 12 , 2015 : By Ted Allen /Liberty University News Service Darryl Strawberry , who won four World Series with the New York Mets and Yankees , didn't find his purpose in life until he surrendered it to Christ,
